Christiansen et al. (2015) investigated the relationship between enclosure time and instrument precisionPrecision and introduced the concept of minimum detectable fluxMinimum Detectable Flux (MDF) (MDF) to determine the lower limit of flux rates that can be achieved with a given measurement precisionPrecision (Eq. 2.7):2.7MDF=AAtcVPART\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
